data.title: Too Phat - KL
data.meta_description: Too Phat - KL - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. The song celebrates Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia and represents the city well. It describes KL as a big city of dreams with hustle and different aspects. The lyrics highlight popular areas in KL like Bukit Bintang, Sg. Wang, Bukit Jalil, Stadium Merdeka and sights like the Petronas Towers. The artist Joe Flizzow raps about his relationship with rap and being a Casanova in KL.
